---
/** 포스트 카드 스켈레톤. 카테고리 이동 시 로딩 상태를 표시한다. */
---

<div class="animate-pulse max-w-[718px] max-h-[404px] lg:max-w-none lg:max-h-none">
  <div class="w-full aspect-7/3 bg-gray-200" />
  <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="h-5 bg-gray-200 rounded w-3/4" />
    <div class="h-4 bg-gray-200 rounded w-full" />
    <div class="h-4 bg-gray-200 rounded w-2/3" />
    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
      <div class="h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded w-20" />
      <div class="h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded w-16" />
      <div class="h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded w-12" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
